{"coredata": {"prism:url": "https://api.elsevier.com/content/article/pii/S0893608007000986", "dc:identifier": "doi:10.1016/j.neunet.2007.07.005", "eid": "1-s2.0-S0893608007000986", "prism:doi": "10.1016/j.neunet.2007.07.005", "pii": "S0893-6080(07)00098-6", "dc:title": "Stability of Cohen\u2013Grossberg neural networks with time-varying delays ", "prism:publicationName": "Neural Networks", "prism:aggregationType": "Journal", "prism:issn": "08936080", "prism:volume": "20", "prism:issueIdentifier": "8", "prism:startingPage": "868", "prism:endingPage": "873", "prism:pageRange": "868-873", "prism:number": "8", "dc:format": "application/json", "prism:coverDate": "2007-10-31", "prism:coverDisplayDate": "October 2007", "prism:copyright": "Copyright \u00a9 2007 Elsevier Ltd. All rights reserved.", "prism:publisher": "Elsevier Ltd.", "dc:creator": [{"@_fa": "true", "$": "Huang, Tingwen"}, {"@_fa": "true", "$": "Chan, Andrew"}, {"@_fa": "true", "$": "Huang, Yu"}, {"@_fa": "true", "$": "Cao, Jinde"}], "dc:description": "\n               Abstract\n               \n                  In this paper, we investigate the existence and stability of the equilibrium point of Cohen\u2013Grossberg neural networks with time-varying delays. Under easily verified conditions, exponential stability is obtained when the delay is finite, while asymptotic stability is obtained when the delay is infinite. Moreover, the stability obtained is robust. The only condition for the delay term is continuity. The results obtained here improve and extend to those in the literature.\n               \n            ", "openaccess": "0", "openaccessArticle": false, "openaccessType": null, "openArchiveArticle": false, "openaccessSponsorName": null, "openaccessSponsorType": null, "openaccessUserLicense": null, "dcterms:subject": [{"@_fa": "true", "$": "Exponential stability"}, {"@_fa": "true", "$": "Asymptotic stability"}, {"@_fa": "true", "$": "Cohen\u2013Grossberg neural networks"}, {"@_fa": "true", "$": "Time-varying delays"}], "link": [{"@href": "https://api.elsevier.com/content/article/pii/S0893608007000986", "@rel": "self", "@_fa": "true"}, {"@href": "https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0893608007000986", "@rel": "scidir", "@_fa": "true"}]}, "scopus-id": "34848827472", "scopus-eid": "2-s2.0-34848827472", "pubmed-id": "17720364", "link": {"@href": "https://api.elsevier.com/content/abstract/scopus_id/34848827472", "@rel": "abstract"}, "originalText": {"xocs:doc": {"xocs:meta": {"xocs:open-access": {"xocs:oa-article-status": {"@is-open-access": "0", "@is-open-archive": "0"}}, "xocs:available-online-date": {"@yyyymmdd": "20070728", "$": "2007-07-28"}}}}}